Chrome extension idea

- query your browsing history for the top 10 most visited sites
- display these in a list and a pie chart
- is there a way to tell how long you've been on a site? Like active time? 
- maybe have a blacklist of sites, and pop up a warning when you are visiting on of them?

Get started: https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/getstarted

Devguide: https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/devguide

This could be a useful API: https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/history

And a useful example: http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/chrome/common/extensions/docs/examples/api/history/showHistory/typedUrls.js?revision=119883

